<h1>Accessibility for Analysts</h1>
<p>Analysts play a key role in identifying accessibility requirements and ensuring they are considered throughout projects.</p>

<h2>How Analysts Support Accessibility</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Include accessibility requirements in project documentation and user stories.</li>
  <li>Consult with users with disabilities during research and requirements gathering.</li>
  <li>Review standards, policies, and regulations for accessibility (e.g., WCAG, government standards).</li>
  <li>Collaborate with designers, developers, and testers to ensure accessibility is addressed at every stage.</li>
  <li>Advocate for accessibility in meetings and project planning.</li>
</ul>

